headline: CVS Health Foundation helps address barriers to care and provides resources for individuals with chronic health conditions in Hartford
summary: The CVS Health® Foundation today announced $2 million in new Health Zones funding to support the Hispanic Health Council's Family Wellness Center and its agency partners, all located in Hartford, Connecticut. This funding will help address critical gaps in the health care and social system for individuals with chronic health conditions by increasing access to comprehensive health care services and resources.
